Question 1. What do you understand by IOC?

Ans.IOC means inversion of control. Moreover it has very importand role in Java.When we progaram in Java and we create an object that is called IOC.




Question 2 .Dependency Injection 


Ans.Depency injection is the technique that makes a class independenc of its depedency.transferring the task of creating the object to someone else and directly using the dependency is called dependency injection.



Qeustion 3 . Life Cycle of Spring Bean


Ans.Bean life cycle is managed by the spring container. When we run the program then, first the spring container gets started. After the container, and then dependencies
    are injected. Finally the bean is destroyed when the spring contianer is closed.